00:24:29,264 --> 00:24:31,825
-It smells so good, Tarn.
-Of course.

266
00:24:32,345 --> 00:24:33,665
Try some.

267
00:24:35,945 --> 00:24:38,544
-How is it?
-Amazing.

268
00:24:39,744 --> 00:24:42,385
How sweet. Now, get back to work.

269
00:24:45,385 --> 00:24:47,105
If Nut had stayed with him,

270
00:24:48,825 --> 00:24:51,264
he might have been happier
than he is with me.

271
